text: Kora Aleksandra Jackowska (Sipowicz) (8 June 1951 – 28 July 2018) was a Polish singer, musician, composer, voice actress and TV presenter. She was born in Kraków, Poland. She was the lead singer of the Polish rock band Maanam. Jackowska was the voice of Edna Mode in the Polish language dub of The Incredibles. Jackowska died from ovarian cancer in Bliżów, Poland on 28 July 2018, at the age of 67.
